{"id": "1400402669889126420", "channel_id": "1400402669889126420", "type": 0, "author_id": "1006995420439908363", "author_name": "sshenhuaa", "author_bot": false, "content": "I used emergency gnosis for stage 9-3 on hard mode but still got the achievement (probably shouldn’t have claimed it <:scared2:1356085635374383145> )", "timestamp": "2025-07-31T09:00:14.725000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [{"id": "1400402670426128434", "filename": "IMG_4070.png", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 1653272, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1400402669889126420/1400402670426128434/IMG_4070.png?ex=69cc35de&is=69cae45e&hm=727c7b3484439625cd5e29f2fe98aa447ffaf7b66a1ad2aaaa4e23f27d5d57b1&"}, {"id": "1400402670967062658", "filename": "IMG_4071.png", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 1113193, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1400402669889126420/1400402670967062658/IMG_4071.png?ex=69cc35de&is=69cae45e&hm=11777644046b5443766cda89805f6d6c950412f6dd19490c17331835f3ce4db1&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1400402669889126420", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "💭「Processing」H9-3 achievement bug", "forum_channel_id": "1180845276823564288", "thread_tags": ["1361168893200044183"]}
{"id": "1400503916097048597", "channel_id": "1400402669889126420", "type": 0, "author_id": "1006995420439908363", "author_name": "sshenhuaa", "author_bot": false, "content": "Just realised that my first attempt (which gave me the achievement) did not consume anything while after a second one my gnosis count went down. So I think it was a one time thing but I have no idea what caused it or how to replicate it sorry.", "timestamp": "2025-07-31T15:42:33.702000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1400402669889126420", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "💭「Processing」H9-3 achievement bug", "forum_channel_id": "1180845276823564288", "thread_tags": ["1361168893200044183"]}
{"id": "1400471670514258041", "channel_id": "1400471670514258041", "type": 0, "author_id": "618475034465533954", "author_name": "silencio3507", "author_bot": false, "content": "So ever since the begging I had issue where I had to click multiple times on the title screen for the game to register it, but today I think it's close to few mintues. It's getting longer and longer I fear. What is the issue with it? I'm playing on Steam, my internet connection is good, my system easily meets all the requirements.", "timestamp": "2025-07-31T13:34:25.756000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1400471670514258041", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "💭「Processing」Issue with logging in", "forum_channel_id": "1180845276823564288", "thread_tags": ["1361168893200044183"]}
{"id": "1400608971424796712", "channel_id": "1396994128838918255", "type": 19, "author_id": "461976576804782100", "author_name": "koharyy", "author_bot": false, "content": "I managed to solve the problem, although I had never encountered it before, even though I have played a lot of games. I had to dig into the scaling settings in the Nvidia panel and enable scaling only through the display, and the scaling mode must be set to full screen.\nBy default, I had selected the scaling mode via the video card, and I also had to disable vertical synchronisation in the monitor settings. I don't really understand what exactly caused this strange problem, but now everything works. Perhaps this information will also be useful to someone else later on", "timestamp": "2025-07-31T22:40:00.844000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": ["1131790839291596841"], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": "1399642588079849533", "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1396994128838918255", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "💭「Processing」I can't start the game, it freezes", "forum_channel_id": "1180845276823564288", "thread_tags": ["1361169005435420785", "1361168893200044183"]}
